nodes.text: Knights of the Old Republic Miniatures Preview 5

Knights of the Old Republic Miniatures Preview 5 is the fifth preview article of Wizards of the Coast Knights of the Old Republic miniatures game, written by Sterling Hershey. The article consists of the game cards for Captain Quarsh Panaka and Echani Handmaiden.
Handmaiden's card has mention of the handmaiden Brianna joining the Jedi Exile in her adventures.
